Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:14.93,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:15.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.80,0:00:18.91,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.43,0:00:22.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:26.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:30.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:34.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:36.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:40.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.32,0:00:45.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:48.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:51.20,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:54.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:59.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:03.01,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.51,0:01:11.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:13.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.40,0:01:15.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.31,0:01:18.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:24.81,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,140.389)}Rock Monster Unicornos
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:24.81,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(300,420)}Versus
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:24.81,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(447.167,720.389)}the Double Rider Kick
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.92,0:01:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparations are all complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.42,0:01:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let us begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dissolve the powdered blood we\Nrecovered from the unicorn fossil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... we'll use it to make this\Nevil man into the cyborg Unicornos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Initiate the blood\Ntransfer at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Good... the surgery is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Letter from Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?\NEveryone's out today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're hiking\Nto Okutama today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what does it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.24,0:03:36.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"Ichimonji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:41.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,By now I'm sure you've heard of the\Nrecent discovery in Europe of a fossil
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:45.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,belonging to that one-horned beast\Nwritten of in Greek and Roman legend:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:47.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,a unicorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:49.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I'm sending a picture\Nof the fossil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:54.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately,\Nsomeone stole the fossil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:58.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I just received word that it was\Nrecently brought to Japan by Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.91,0:04:01.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,My dear friend Ichimonji Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:05.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I'm sending you this warning\Nfrom far-away Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:10.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Keep an eye on Shocker's Japan Branch\Nnow that they have the unicorn fossil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:11.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,See you around."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Damned Shocker... \NWhat are they plotting this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, want to go in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an7\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Hibara Limestone Cavern
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet we'll find Hell\NValley, the Sanzu River,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and even Sainokawara!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.59,0:04:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's down that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:04:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It says "White-Robed Kannon!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this a dead-end?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very disturbing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like an animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's coming closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it...\NYou're a Shocker cyborg, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll show\Nyou what I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.59,0:05:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Tachibana Raci...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops? This is Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.43,0:05:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro and Emi went missing?\NWhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The limestone caverns?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Emi! Emi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.18,0:06:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to drag you out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We've searched everywhere\Nand can't find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you looked over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They couldn't fit in there.\NIt's too small!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But we should\Nlook, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Taki.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:06:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,These are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are Goro and Emi's shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems unbelievable,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think these\Nare Goro and Emi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You think they've\Nbeen frozen over?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No... this isn't ice, but rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's take them to\NDoctor Oshita's laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They're playing\Nright into my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll teach you a\Nlesson very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:40.10,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\fs60\c&H2F4F5D&\3c&H11190F&}Oshita Institute\Nof Space Research
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not working.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not even making a dent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what is it made of?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's clear that the outer\Nlayer is rock, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:08:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying there's no way to\Nget Goro and Emi out of this rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The super energy beam you just completed\Nwould surely cut through the rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Super energy beam?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I'll never make it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of the beam terrified even\Nme, its creator.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were to fall into the wrong hands,\Nit would mean the end of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I locked the notebook detailing the\Nbeam's creation process in a safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and swore never\Nto open it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.73,0:08:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Unicornos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come\Nfor you to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.69,0:08:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, and steal Oshita's\Nnotebook from that safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker requires the super\Nenergy invented by Oshita
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:09:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to destroy humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Unicornos!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Doctor... you'll create the\Nsuper energy beam for us once more?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I can't argue\Nwith your passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise to create it\Nas quickly as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so we can save your friends\Nencased in the stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My assistant Kobayashi is\Npreparing it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Open it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on! I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm opening it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You tricked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- The laboratory!\N- Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.39,0:10:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocked, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Unicornos.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Unicornos?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.58,0:10:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you their unicorn cyborg?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to steal the secret\Nof the super energy beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come down here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:02.32,Italics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:05.03,Italics,,0,0,0,,We'll finish this another day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:07.91,Italics,,0,0,0,,Be ready! You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... where did he get off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:20.74,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:40.30,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Hibara Limestone Cavern
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... there must be a Shocker\Nbase around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker... show yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Unicornos...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your legs have turned to stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even\Nwalk, let alone run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,These are his notes on\Nthe super energy beam, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo to Ichimonji!\NHongo to Ichimonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato,\NI've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.02,0:15:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you now?\NGive me your location!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,First, track this cycle with\Nyour directional wave detector.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.21,0:15:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It should lead you to\NShocker and Unicornos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to destroy him. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...\Nminus seven degrees, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... through here, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've stolen the notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.95,0:16:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Unicornos.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we will be able to\Ncreate the super energy beam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a mini-transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.16,0:16:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wretched Kamen Rider...\Nhe set us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he trying to\Nlocate our hideout?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to\Nworry, though, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He's currently...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.47,0:17:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look so surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more than\None Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're back in Japan, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.46,0:17:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here from Europe\Nto destroy Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him! Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.39,0:18:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.17,0:18:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You handle them, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,See to it, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.51,0:18:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, you will pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me that notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll turn you into stone, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Unicornos!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.26,0:21:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where has Unicornos gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.96,0:21:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Double Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Unicornos became a fossil again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.28,0:21:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.16,0:22:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.32,0:22:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.25,0:22:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're leaving again\Nwithout seeing the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.00,0:22:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.51,0:22:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's got more plans for\NEurope, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe it'll be\Nmy turn to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.69,0:22:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.55,0:22:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Look after the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.84,0:22:55.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami's plans to steal the\Nsecrets of the super energy beam
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.97,0:22:58.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,were crushed by the\Ntwo Kamen Riders.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.17,0:23:02.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker wasn't\Nabout to relent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.56,0:23:06.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Where would they strike next?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:10.51,Cont,,0,50,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:14.10,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:14.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.51,0:23:16.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monster bird Gillgaras.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.22,0:23:18.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The "dead man gas" it breathes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.70,0:23:21.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,turns people into mindless killers\Nwho try to murder indiscriminately.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.31,0:23:25.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker plans to use this gas\Nto destroy all of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.20,0:23:26.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.63,0:23:30.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "My Name is Monster Bird Gillgaras!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:30.90,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(447.167,245.389)}My Name is
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:30.90,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,700.389)}Monster Bird Gillgaras!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.90,0:23:40.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.32,0:23:43.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.32,0:23:45.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.28,0:23:48.33,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.83,0:23:50.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.70,0:23:52.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.58,0:23:54.37,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:55.82,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.21,0:23:58.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.26,0:24:03.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.98,0:24:07.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.51,0:24:11.11,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.56,0:24:15.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock Monster Unicornos\NVersus the Double Rider Kick
Comment: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:30.90,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,720.389)}My Name is\N Monster Bird Gillgaras!